ef=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 18, 2026</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104arw1665703179582.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/arw1665703179582.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/arw1665703179582.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"arw1665703179582\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Decode a null terminated Base64 encoded string to string.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"arw1665703179582__topic_d132659e1_d132660e1_d132661e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"arw1665703179582__p_d132662e1_d132663e1_d132664e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">extern long UBase64Dec(const unsigned char *</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">In</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, unsigned char *</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Out</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, long</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OutMaxLen</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">);</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"arw1665703179582__section_w4371ab1b5b3_w4372ab1b5_w4373ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d839850e77\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Parameter</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Direction</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">In</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">IN</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Base64 encoded string that is to be decoded</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Out</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">OUT</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Decoded result</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OutMaxLen</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">IN</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15818e1_d15819e1_d15820e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Maximum number of bytes that can be written to <var class=\"keyword varname\">Out</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"arw1665703179582__section_w4374ab1b5b5_w4375ab1b5_w4376ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d839850e197\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15833e1_d15834e1_d15835e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15833e1_d15834e1_d15835e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15833e1_d15834e1_d15835e1__entry__2\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15833e1_d15834e1_d15835e1__entry__1\">&lt; 0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15833e1_d15834e1_d15835e1__entry__2\">Not all characters have been\n                    decoded.<p class=\"p\">(<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code> x <var class=\"keyword varname\">ReturnValue</var>) have been\n                  decoded.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15833e1_d15834e1_d15835e1__entry__1\"> 0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15833e1_d15834e1_d15835e1__entry__2\">Failed to decode in base64</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15833e1_d15834e1_d15835e1__entry__1\">&gt; 0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_d15833e1_d15834e1_d15835e1__entry__2\">All characters have been decoded. The value is the\n                actual length of the output data.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"arw1665703179582__section_w4377ab1b5b7_w4378ab1b5_w4379ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d839850e264\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"arw1665703179582__p_d132800e1_d132801e1_d132802e1\">Library <span class=\"ph filepath\">uenc</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"arw1665703179582__section_w4380ab1b5b9_w4381ab1b5_w4382ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d839850e276\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"arw1665703179582__p_d132647e1_d132648e1_d132649e1\">This function is useful for creating security drivers\n        that need to encode and decode data.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"arw1665703179582__section_qjz_jq1_4cc\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_evy_ypg_q3c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Related learning videos</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Title</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"arw1665703179582__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">link</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Using $decode to decode base64 data</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"arw1665703179582__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/1147371590\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Watch or listen using $decode to decode base64 data video\" class=\"image\" id=\"arw1665703179582__image_nvt_tfg_q3c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Video_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ufm1665703179207.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UBase64Enc</a><p>Encode a null terminated string in Base64 format.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525856\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525856\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UBase64Dec Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 18, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Decode a null terminated Base64 encoded string to string. extern long UBase64Dec(const unsigned char * In , unsigned char * Out , long OutMaxLen ); Parameters Parameter Direction Description In IN Base64 encoded string that is to be decoded Out OUT Decoded result OutMaxLen IN Maximum number of bytes that can be written to Out Return Values Value Meaning < 0 Not all characters have been decoded. ( -1 x ReturnValue ) have been decoded. 0 Failed to decode in base64 > 0 All characters have been decoded. The value is the actual length of the output data. Use Library uenc Description This function is useful for creating security drivers that need to encode and decode data. Table 1. Related learning videos Title link Using $decode to decode base64 data Related Links UBase64Enc Encode a null terminated string in Base64 format. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}